These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, oliveros
City: liverpool, colone
2 different games are played: domino, go
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog
1. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the person traveling to colone##8
2. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
3. the dannemann-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Cigar      | oliveros     | dannemann      |
| City          | colone | liverpool    |
| Game         | go   | domino |
| Pet   | chinchilla  | dog      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, french
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall
House: palace, craftsman
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
1. the french is on the far right##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
3. the craftsman house is not to the right of the palace house##8
4. the owner of the chinchilla is not the pall-mall-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Nationality    | italian        | french    |
| Cigar       | aristoff         | pall-mall |
| House         | craftsman | palace   |
| Pet   | chinchilla               | horse  |

