.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy
City: venice, paris
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, bus
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, soccer
1. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
3. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Flower   | daisy       | poppy |
| City   | venice       | paris    |
| Transport   | taxi | bus |
| Sport           | baseball        | soccer   |

