.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, cycling
2 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret
2 different games are played: canasta, go
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, june
1. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
2. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Sport         | cycling | sailing  |
| Pet           | ferret  | lizard |
| Game   | go | canasta   |
| Birthday     | june   | december |

