2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, swisher
There 2 different types of food: carrot, pineapple
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
2. the person eating carrot is not to the right of the siglo-smoker##8
3. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Flower   | lily | begonia |
| Cigar   | swisher    | siglo     |
| Food         | carrot  | pineapple    |
| Beverage     | juice     | milk       |

